seven-colored radiance under sunlight.

862
00:38:44,230 --> 00:38:46,360
It's truly a wonder of the world.

863
00:38:46,710 --> 00:38:48,510
I had planned to wait until
Your Majesty's birthday

864
00:38:48,510 --> 00:38:49,960
