894
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:08,320
Tell Yin

895
00:40:09,150 --> 00:40:11,280
to prepare the gastrodia powder soon.

896
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:12,670
Yes.

897
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:24,670
Do you like this one?

898
00:40:24,920 --> 00:40:25,920
