Trinkets!

903
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:46,880
All kinds of trinkets!

904
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,720
Sachets and pendants!

905
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:50,880
Take a look!

906
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:52,510
Look around!

907
00:40:58,000 --> 00:40:59,000
